<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 01:32:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>男子注定因意外热疗而得阿尔茨海默氏症</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/man-destined-to-get-alzheimers-saved-by-accidental-heat-therapy</link><description>道格·惠特尼（Doug Whitney）患有基因突变，这意味着他几十年前就应该患上阿尔茨海默病，但他长期在高温机房工作可能以类似于桑拿疗法的方式保护了他&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/man-destined-to-get-alzheimers-saved-by-accidental-heat-therapy.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 01:32:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/man-destined-to-get-alzheimers-saved-by-accidental-heat-therapy</guid></item><item><title>科学家刚刚发现地球实际上来自哪里</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/scientists-just-discovered-where-the-earth-actually-came-from</link><description>科学家们似乎已经解决了关于地球组成部分是否起源于内太阳系或外太阳系的长期争论。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-just-discovered-where-the-earth-actually-came-from.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 01:17:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/scientists-just-discovered-where-the-earth-actually-came-from</guid></item><item><title>300 年历史的实验可能成为世界上最好的暗物质探测器</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/300-year-old-experiment-could-become-worlds-best-dark-matter-detector</link><description>亨利·卡文迪什 (Henry Cavendish) 在 1773 年进行的一项实验的更新可能是一种更便宜、更快速的发现潜在暗物质粒子的方法，而且灵敏度可能提高 10,000 倍&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/300-year-old-experiment-could-become-worlds-best-dark-matter-detector.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 01:02:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/300-year-old-experiment-could-become-worlds-best-dark-matter-detector</guid></item><item><title>为什么现实不仅仅是其粒子的总和</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/why-reality-is-more-than-the-sum-of-its-particles</link><description>富恩特：永旺&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/why-reality-is-more-than-the-sum-of-its-particles.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 00:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/why-reality-is-more-than-the-sum-of-its-particles</guid></item><item><title>科学家发现，人类心脏在受到攻击后可以再生肌肉</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/human-heart-can-regrow-muscle-after-attack-scientists-find</link><description>科学家发现人类心脏在心脏病发作后可以再生肌肉细胞，为再生疗法开辟了道路。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/human-heart-can-regrow-muscle-after-attack-scientists-find.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 00:32:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/human-heart-can-regrow-muscle-after-attack-scientists-find</guid></item><item><title>一神论、怀疑论和新的后人类女神和众神</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/monotheism-scepticism-and-new-posthuman-goddesses-and-gods</link><description>古埃及提供了一个宽容的、非一神论社会的优秀历史模式，培育了复杂的哲学和宗教框架。在这个文明中，万神殿并不被视为相互排斥、嫉妒的神灵的集合，而是被视为单一的、潜在的宇宙秩序的多方面表达，称为Ma&amp;#39;at（真理、平衡和正义）。埃及诸神并不是遥远的、超然的立法者，而是嵌入自然和社会世界的动态的、内在的力量。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/monotheism-scepticism-and-new-posthuman-goddesses-and-gods.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 00:17:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/monotheism-scepticism-and-new-posthuman-goddesses-and-gods</guid></item><item><title>科学家将 3D 打印的可弯曲软传感器植入每个大脑褶皱中，为个性化神经学开辟了新途径</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/scientists-3d-printed-bendable-soft-sensors-into-every-brain-fold-opening-a-new-path-for-personalized-neurology</link><description>一项新研究发现，软质 3D 打印大脑传感器比标准刚性设备能够更紧密地追踪个体大脑褶皱。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-3d-printed-bendable-soft-sensors-into-every-brain-fold-opening-a-new-path-for-personalized-neurology.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 00:02:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/scientists-3d-printed-bendable-soft-sensors-into-every-brain-fold-opening-a-new-path-for-personalized-neurology</guid></item><item><title>表观遗传皮肤老化及其逆转，使用含二氢杨梅素的血清改善不同种族和光型的皮肤寿命：前瞻性、单队列研究的结果 — Dermatology and Therapy</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/epigenetic-skin-aging-and-its-reversal-to-improve-skin-longevity-across-ethnicities-and-phototypes-using-a-dihydromyricetin-containing-serum-results-from-a-prospective-single-cohort-study</link><description>皮肤老化是由内在和外在因素驱动的。表观遗传改变是衰老的主要标志之一，也是生物皮肤年龄的强大生物标志物。为了研究表观遗传皮肤衰老机制及其调节作为不同种族和光型皮肤长寿的方法，我们评估了白人、非洲和亚洲供体的表皮甲基化组。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/epigenetic-skin-aging-and-its-reversal-to-improve-skin-longevity-across-ethnicities-and-phototypes-using-a-dihydromyricetin-containing-serum-results-from-a-prospective-single-cohort-study.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 23:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/epigenetic-skin-aging-and-its-reversal-to-improve-skin-longevity-across-ethnicities-and-phototypes-using-a-dihydromyricetin-containing-serum-results-from-a-prospective-single-cohort-study</guid></item><item><title>CATL的新型电动汽车电池只需六分钟即可充电</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/catls-new-ev-battery-charges-in-six-minutes</link><description>这比普通汽油动力汽车加满油所需的时间要长几分钟，但仍然足够快，这可能并不重要。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/catls-new-ev-battery-charges-in-six-minutes2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 23:32:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/catls-new-ev-battery-charges-in-six-minutes</guid></item><item><title>研究发现，基于 DNA 的新疗法无需他汀类药物即可帮助降低“坏胆固醇”</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/new-dna-based-therapy-can-help-lower-bad-cholesterol-without-statins-finds-study</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 23:17:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/new-dna-based-therapy-can-help-lower-bad-cholesterol-without-statins-finds-study</guid></item></channel></rss>